rem Outside Hosaka
rem 8/17/2017

items screen

do Examine Hosaka Industries
 [
  ifflag hosaka alarm
   [
    print The large warehouse doesn't blend very well, with alarms sounding and
    print security trying to contain the event. Scientists from Hosaka don't know
    print what to do, watching as security enters the building.
   |
    print It's a large warehouse that blends into the urban landscape. Non descript,
    print the only thing different about it is the security that's set up outside.
   ]
 ]

do Enter Hosaka Industries
 [
  ifflag hosaka alarm
   [
    print That would be a bad idea, security is trying to get hold of the situation.
   |
    ifitemin shuriken,INV
     [
      print You'd only set off the alarm holding on to the shuriken.
     |
      ifitemin id badge,INV
       [
        ifflag wear badge
         [
          ifflag badge imprinted
           [
            print You stroll through, setting off no alarms.
            go Hosaka Lobby
           |
            print You'd only set off the alarm with the wrong D.N.A. imprint.
           ]
         |
          print You need to put the badge on if you're going to walk behind the screen.
         ]
       |
        print You at least need an id badge if you're going to try to sleaze your way past
        print security.
       ]
     ]
   ]
 ]

do Walk South
 [
  print You walk south to Hakaru Station.
  go Hakaru Station
 ]